# Konzola

Don't forget to install the custom terminfo entry:

```
    sudo tic -sx st.info
```

Installation:

```
    make clean
    make
```

After this, if you have been making changes you can run the terminal to check their effect.

```
    st
```

And finally, installing the terminal:

````
    sudo make install
```
````
